    phaseImage: {fileID: 2800000, guid: 95c9251ea87007148b6dd477cc90a1c9, type: 3}
    phaseDesc: 'I stood for a moment, overlooking the valley stretched before me.
      Sunlight glistened on the drops of dew. My sneakers were soaked with morning
      frost. Birds swooped from the heavens and purple flowers sprung up on the carpet
      of grass. The euphoria overtook me. I wanted to be in this serene pocket of
      the universe for the rest of my life. '
